<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dokumentasi API - Cloudku</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Kembali ke Home</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <h1>Dokumentasi API Cloudku</h1>
        <p>Gunakan endpoint berikut untuk integrasi aplikasi pihak ketiga.</p>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Upload File</h2>
            <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>POST /upload</code></p>
            <p><strong>Method:</strong> <code>multipart/form-data</code></p>
            <p><strong>Field:</strong> <code>file</code> (Binary)</p>
        </section>

        <hr>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Akses File (Proxy)</h2>
            <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>GET /f/:filename</code></p>
            <p>Sistem akan mencari file di database Turso dan melakukan <i>streaming</i> langsung dari CloudSky.</p>
        </section>

        <section style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; background: #eee; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h3>Catatan Developer</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Database: Turso (LibSQL)</li>
                <li>Storage: CloudSky</li>
                <li>Proxying: Node-fetch Stream</li>
                <li>Limit: 200MB</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
